text: Andlang englunga dene swa wæter wile yrnan in hæþenan byrigels a be wyrtwalan in barfodslæd and swa on timberslæd in stepacnolles scydd on hanslædes heafdan<../images/tbar.gif>innan grenan weg.
Þanon innan healde mæres hlinc in stanora lege<../images/tbar.gif>in stanmeres hlinc on catedenes heafdan<../images/tbar.gif>in holemeres hlinc innan stanbeorh.

And swa in smalan æsc in þonne mapultre on west healf assundene from þam mapoltre in edles pyt<../images/tbar.gif>in dragmæres hlinc swa in rugawic in deopan hamsteale on hremhryc<../images/tbar.gif>in þone fulan slo to sigordene.
Swa in badan dene in clacces wadlond.
And swa into lufan mere þær ut on þæne feld on grottes graf<../images/tbar.gif>in ceorla pytte to þære fleotan<../images/tbar.gif>on crawan þorn on þonne hæð on hweolriðig.
Swa on morpyt on senthylle in hroppan broc a be broce on þa ealdan dic<../images/tbar.gif>on crypsan hylle on scyttan mere<../images/tbar.gif>on scyttan dune.
Swa on smalan broc to Cnihtabryge & swa to winecalea on þæne hæþena byregels in colnaran.
